SIMPLE: pitiless
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pitiless
<hw>Pit"i*less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Destitute of pity;
hard-hearted; merciless; <as>as, a <ex>pitiless</ex>master;
<ex>pitiless</ex> elements.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Exciting no pity; <as>as, a <ex>pitiless</ex>
condition</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Pit"i*less*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Pit"i*less*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pitman</ent>⟦br⟧
